Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.00,0:01:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托了 拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.77,0:01:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这事实在太丢脸 没法告诉健二他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.44,0:01:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我觉得不说的话你又不能理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.75,0:01:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我觉得很不愉快 不能原谅那女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.06,0:01:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.12,0:01:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别把真子想那么坏 她是个好女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.01,0:01:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么前辈要袒护那女人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.80,0:02:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不明白 前辈你没必要做到这个份上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.95,0:02:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托了 拓海 请你理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.17,0:02:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了 拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.85,0:02:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是第一次来秋名以外的山道吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.53,0:02:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么样? 能跑吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.04,0:02:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那种事不跑怎么知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.42,0:02:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会去跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.45,0:02:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.37,0:02:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 承你恩情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.88,0:02:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然无法理解前辈和那女人是什么情况...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.47,0:02:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.57,0:02:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总之我会开86去碓冰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.90,0:03:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\pos(147,116)\fs20\fad(650,750)}骤死赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.87,0:03:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的吗? 健二前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.15,0:03:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海那小子要和碓冰山道的Sil-80比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.64,0:03:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难以置信啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.07,0:03:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.78,0:03:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他应该不是那种主动跑去别的山道比赛的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.64,0:03:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,池谷前辈是怎么拜托他的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.42,0:03:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不太清楚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.14,0:03:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,详情池谷那小子没告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.70,0:03:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前他曾说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.74,0:03:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没在秋名以外跑过的拓海 在别的山道会有何表现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.46,0:03:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道不理解那想见识一下的心情吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.50,0:03:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可也不能马上就和当地最快的Sil-80比赛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.48,0:03:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海要去碓冰比赛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.43,0:03:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊 店长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.92,0:03:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对方的Sil-80有那么厉害?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.79,0:03:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经不是厉害的问题了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.56,0:04:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那狭窄的碓冰道路上自由自在地卖弄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.08,0:04:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连假动作都用上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.90,0:04:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海也一起看过那Sil-80 不可能不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.77,0:04:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但拓海的话会赢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.70,0:04:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总是像你这么乐观可真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.06,0:04:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当地也无人能赢 加油站的小哥不也这么说过吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.30,0:04:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说不定拓海...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.15,0:04:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从一开始就将胜负置之度外而去比赛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.61,0:04:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦? 不好 抽光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.75,0:04:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开86去买点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.40,0:04:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么情况?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.23,0:04:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,86变85了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.35,0:04:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,车借一下 留这个代替
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.99,0:05:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在你老爸肯定在惊讶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.70,0:05:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,86不知何时变成了我的85
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.89,0:05:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,池谷 有件事想问你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.46,0:05:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.76,0:05:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天的比赛你帮哪一边?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.70,0:05:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,问我帮哪边...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.73,0:05:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是比赛的中间人 两不相帮...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.30,0:05:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这话当真?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.66,0:05:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想过拓海的立场吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.05,0:05:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你小子是不是光顾着真子的漂亮脸蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.91,0:05:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,眼里已经容不下朋友了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.25,0:05:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪有这回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.54,0:05:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.56,0:05:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那告诉我 你觉得拓海有胜算吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.07,0:05:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么样? 池谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.71,0:05:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明确回答我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.29,0:06:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.04,0:06:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能赢的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.99,0:06:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只熟悉秋名山道的拓海...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.39,0:06:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在生平第一次跑的碓冰...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.95,0:06:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那么困难的赛道上...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.04,0:06:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然那小子技术超群
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.82,0:06:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但也有凭技术无法解决的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.24,0:06:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是赛道熟悉程度的问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.07,0:06:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,练习也没有就直接动真格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.48,0:06:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是拓海也毫无胜算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.49,0:06:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不可能连这个都不清楚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.19,0:06:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.87,0:06:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是 所有男人对自己喜欢的女人都很软弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.12,0:06:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作为车手日子里最后夏天的回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.07,0:06:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请让我和秋名的86在碓冰山道比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.78,0:06:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但你别做出为讨好女人而出卖朋友的举动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.20,0:07:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你忘了拓海和86在最困难的时候帮过你吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.04,0:07:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,秋名的86是我们的骄傲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.31,0:07:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种比赛可以放弃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.90,0:07:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不然...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.01,0:07:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就和你绝交
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.31,0:07:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,健二 明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.02,0:07:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.72,0:07:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该更早点和你商量的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.21,0:07:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过我一个人考虑了很久...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.46,0:07:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.53,0:07:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么不做车手?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.37,0:07:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,两年前 刚开始飙车时快乐得忘乎所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.15,0:08:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直以本地第一作为目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.83,0:08:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在也很快乐 不是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.11,0:08:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么说呢 现在没有了那时候的紧张感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.77,0:08:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不知道是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.70,0:08:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我觉得差不多是时候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.65,0:08:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到此为止就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.64,0:08:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗? 不说清楚让我很不痛快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.46,0:08:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想交个男朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.77,0:08:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尝试一下像沙雪这样普通的恋爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.27,0:08:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我觉得车手也一样能交到男朋友啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.50,0:08:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行啊 我想沙雪你不会明白我的感受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.30,0:08:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你其实有了喜欢的男人了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.87,0:09:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我坦白 有个人我思慕了很久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.08,0:09:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.17,0:09:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是瞎猜的 这事还是第一次听到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.48,0:09:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想沙雪你也不会明白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.57,0:09:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不是附近的人 只是我单方面地远距离思慕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.25,0:09:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那算什么 该说你是少女情趣还是晚熟?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.82,0:09:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都二十岁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.97,0:09:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么关系 只是思慕着就满足了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.01,0:09:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是思慕?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.19,0:09:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你必须面对现实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.96,0:09:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.54,0:09:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可我和沙雪这两年的持续努力究竟到了什么程度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.76,0:10:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想在最后的比赛中验证一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.64,0:10:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,意味着告别过去呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.27,0:10:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对你来说很不错 完全够格做真子的对手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.45,0:10:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是丑话说在前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.69,0:10:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在碓冰山道比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.51,0:10:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管对手是谁 输了的话是绝不能原谅的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.48,0:10:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不然的话我绝不同意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.43,0:10:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.43,0:10:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们是非赢不可的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.05,0:10:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算对手是秋名86
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.11,0:10:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绝对可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.40,0:10:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是这么回事 不想比赛的话别勉强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.17,0:10:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和池谷会和对方说清楚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.19,0:10:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在下个出口回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.45,0:10:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就这么办吧 麻烦你了 拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.22,0:10:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原谅他吧 拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.63,0:10:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,健二前辈 我不想回去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.04,0:11:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.10,0:11:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想比赛才去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.71,0:11:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是我自己的意志 没打算过要回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.05,0:11:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.44,0:11:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.87,0:11:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也见过真子的实力 应该明白吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.97,0:11:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么想也太不合算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.79,0:11:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是你也没有胜算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.43,0:11:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.25,0:11:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胜负对我来说无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.85,0:11:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么可以 你别说得那么轻松
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.05,0:11:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说到秋名86 现在可是轰动一时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.51,0:11:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你应该自重点才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.65,0:11:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不太擅长那样 碰巧都在本地所以才赢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.61,0:11:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虚名在外的话感觉很难受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.11,0:11:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那种传闻早点消散反而更痛快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.59,0:11:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么会...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.35,0:11:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.54,0:12:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只想在第一次跑的山道上尽情挑战一番而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.92,0:12:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思 池谷 刚才说得太过份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.93,0:12:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,经拓海那么一说 我们也没话好说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.42,0:12:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海真是个不可思议的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.92,0:12:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,该说他是和我们想法不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.89,0:12:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是实力过人的表现呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.96,0:12:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难以理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.84,0:12:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,轮胎没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.55,0:12:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这种山道情况下最有抓地力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.18,0:12:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,悬挂也不用改
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.16,0:12:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照现在这样就是最棒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.15,0:12:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沙雪说的绝不会错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.65,0:12:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想你也应该明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.30,0:13:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真正比赛时不能用大角度的漂移
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.86,0:13:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有可滑和不可滑弯道的灵活运用也是关键
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.48,0:13:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特别是在这连续弯较多的碓冰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.81,0:13:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有我在 你只要相信自己的技术全力前进就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.12,0:13:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会输给任何人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.11,0:13:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下定决心了 包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.46,0:13:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我们是二位一体的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.62,0:13:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我热血沸腾了 沙雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.78,0:13:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今晚展现出迄今为止的最强跑法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.78,0:13:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好期待哦 真兴奋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.71,0:13:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会是场什么样的比赛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.36,0:13:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会是个什么样的对手?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.10,0:14:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海 怎么才能取胜?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.24,0:14:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么战术? 告诉我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.92,0:14:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.58,0:14:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那算什么 什么办法都没有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.22,0:14:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不想看到你输啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.35,0:14:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.04,0:14:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,碓冰很狭窄 也没什么直路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.80,0:14:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以呢...抢跑一点占住先机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.16,0:14:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这算什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.33,0:14:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后就堵在路中间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.64,0:14:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不让她超车地跑下去 不就赢了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.91,0:14:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那样太卑鄙了 不可能这么做吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.78,0:14:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可让她占了先机甩开的话就输了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.95,0:14:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,话说的没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.27,0:14:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没什么好的战术吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.68,0:14:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都是装了四个轮胎的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.98,0:15:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真是86的车手!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.76,0:15:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有点难以置信 你几岁了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.43,0:15:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十八了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.55,0:15:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十八...高中生...饶了我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.84,0:15:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们也才二十而已 我觉得也够年轻的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.54,0:15:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且还是女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.48,0:15:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,年纪小的话就更加不能输了 真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.25,0:15:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就切入正题吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.17,0:15:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比赛的方法是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.70,0:16:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并排起步的方法不太适合这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.15,0:16:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为出发后抢得先机的人就完全占了上风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.94,0:16:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像这样狡猾地比谁抢跑快的比赛令人厌恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.74,0:16:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个战术不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.32,0:16:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那...怎么比?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.61,0:16:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先行后追的比赛 明白吗? 就是追逐赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.82,0:16:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先行者将后追者甩开就算赢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.35,0:16:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无法甩开的话再互换位置 直到决出胜负为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.11,0:16:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是骤死赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.65,0:16:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.82,0:16:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.59,0:16:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们是主场 所以第一轮位置的选择权在你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.72,0:16:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决定前后吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.81,0:16:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.83,0:16:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来这边 拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.01,0:16:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种规则的话 第一轮肯定选先行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.52,0:16:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为能确保拖延到第二轮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.67,0:16:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且有一轮可以练习
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.61,0:16:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二轮输了也没那么难看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.73,0:17:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正第一轮对方会选先行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.96,0:17:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在第二轮决胜负 别担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.68,0:17:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难得大家费心建议 但不好意思...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.01,0:17:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前辈 我不喜欢那样做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.62,0:17:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在说什么啊 拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.46,0:17:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一轮我从后面出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.24,0:17:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.40,0:17:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再想想清楚 拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.19,0:17:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是我的比赛 我自己会决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.57,0:17:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.54,0:17:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从后面出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.06,0:17:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,后面?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.67,0:17:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他到底是嚣张还是笨蛋?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.99,0:17:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也好 甩开他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.61,0:17:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁啊 空不出手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.00,0:18:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里是藤原豆腐店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.07,0:18:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 文太吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.76,0:18:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了 是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.60,0:18:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.85,0:18:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有件事我很关心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.11,0:18:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实是拓海那小子...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.67,0:18:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差不多了 要开始啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.50,0:18:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去碓冰山道比赛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.89,0:18:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦 这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.73,0:18:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“哦 这样啊”你要说的就这些?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.36,0:18:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不担心吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.46,0:18:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,担心什么 他可是我儿子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.84,0:18:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们会慢慢出发 别心急 跟在后面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.34,0:18:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,过了第一个弯就会全力加速冲刺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.66,0:18:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是比赛开始的信号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.03,0:19:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就这些 没别的了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.67,0:19:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就这些 我很忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.08,0:19:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没什么事就别打电话来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.87,0:19:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,文太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.50,0:19:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海 我是个笨蛋 到现在才醒悟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.89,0:19:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我应该明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.06,0:19:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你为了我的面子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.65,0:19:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早知会输
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.06,0:19:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,却还是接受了这种无理的比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.44,0:19:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我现在非常后悔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.14,0:19:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可是我们所有秋名车手的骄傲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.01,0:19:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我做了无法挽回的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.17,0:19:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想看到你这样不明不白地输掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.15,0:19:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海不会输的 前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.99,0:19:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说是这么说 但现实是残酷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.18,0:20:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.69,0:20:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,池谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.03,0:20:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前辈 我是考虑过了才选后追的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.32,0:20:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.07,0:20:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽不知能否取胜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.61,0:20:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我从一开始就没想过要输
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.33,0:20:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海 有什么战术?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.66,0:20:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谈不上什么战术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.98,0:20:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是非常单纯的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.58,0:20:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么想法? 拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.77,0:20:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告诉我们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.85,0:20:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论对方的车有多快 也不可能飞上天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.88,0:20:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同样都是车子 装了四个轮胎的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.23,0:20:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以 对方能转的弯道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.42,0:20:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我应该也能用同样的速度来转
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.38,0:20:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是这样想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.82,0:20:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.41,0:20:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,理论上是没错...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.85,0:21:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那也太乱来了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.38,0:21:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要出发了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.90,0:21:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 上吧 真子 一轮就结束这场比赛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.28,0:21:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 沙雪 展现出迄今为止的最强跑法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.91,0:22:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,两车都是全油门跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.57,0:22:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,终于开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.26,0:22:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海的第一次客场比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.11,0:22:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 就算是拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.37,0:22:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比赛的条件也太过艰难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.00,0:22:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没关系 没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.04,0:22:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海绝对会赢啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:25.81,0:24:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真子 主场是绝不能输的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:29.01,0:24:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我们是车手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:31.98,0:24:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请问 沙雪小姐
